programme.desc: «America's Most Expensive Zip Code & The $1,000,000 Junker»Attend an open house in America's new most expensive zip code. See how a real estate mogul transformed his office into a multi-million dollar car gallery. Find out why investors are betting big on blue stones, including a $17-million diamond. Witness the special delivery of a super-rich car collector's second $4,000,000 Lamborghini. Tour the $50 million mega-mansion where everything is made from raw and organic materials. Smoke the world's most expensive cigars in the hidden stogie room reserved for the rich and famous. And check out the rare Cracker Jack card collection that's worth a fortune.

programme.desc: European Le Mans Series believes in the team spirit during long distance performance.
